95fa6c0811def857f8d8c0accb9133e096c9","tid":1552723,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa31607b15e3f00d77ac46105919c5a12c1363d1","tid":1552723,"uid":237517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連登又光復了"},{"pid":"f37a6e83349ce5458e1dd5fc98d2dd06be2075f4","tid":1552723,"uid":157453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:26:07.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有哂目標就唔怕鬼<br />\n甚至set埋勇武出場條件"},{"pid":"7f5fb85f0ba5ad0ec684d2a98a468cca55d1abd2","tid":1552723,"uid":167394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:27:57.000Z","msg":"早出早歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f8157a9d5169ff59d6e5ac980e816b2ae98ac5","tid":1552723,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:27:59.000Z","msg":"轉發<br />\n我算係條隊嘅中游位，但臨上到美領有班狗set防線唔畀上，然後就有人舉牌話封左中環站，集會取消，唔畀上美領，要係16點30定45分前散。跟住一大班人上唔到美領，焗住落返中環。但中環同香港封站，又焗撚住去金鐘，點知沿途一路話金鐘站大量狗喎。金鐘站係轉地鐵出返去新界九龍嘅站，你佈撚晒防邊個敢去？現場好多人叫唔好坐黨鐵，結果成班走晒去等巴士，但巴士係絕對唔夠散，而且我仲見到班狗開始封路玩管制，即係連巴士都想搞埋。<br />\n我一路行，一路見到有d手足開始上gear，但佢地上完之後係企係原地等和理非散水，有d甚至走返去中環，如果唔係佢地拖時間，一大班和理非將會食tg甚至子彈放題。<br />\n知唔知今日幾多人得d爛鳩醫生口罩？想殺人呀？<br />\n今日係黑警有心玩野，唔好再屌前線。"},{"pid":"942072b99f68af49f468f0fbf1c57ed29217f24a","tid":1552723,"uid":165213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:28:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2e56864a09eab5cc4aea309bb3b0a0a8c2309d8","tid":1552723,"uid":147345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:38:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62f9106bb83e53713bca182fdfa1512651e70130","tid":1552723,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}